NK041(di)029:1: // mnol bsang lha chab sngon mo'i khog dbub spyi chings mdor bsdus bzhugs /
NK041(di)029:2: na mo gu ru pad+m+aa ka ra ye /
NK041(di)029:3: mnol bsang lha chab sngon mo 'di nyid lag tu len pa la /
NK041(di)029:4: sbyor ba gtsang ma'i stegs bu ras dkar gyi khebs dang ldan pa'i khar /
NK041(di)029:5: snod gtsang mar 'bru sna'i phye dang bsang rdzas brgya
NK041(di)029:6: rtsa sogs 'og gi tshig ris dang mthun pa'i sman
NK041(di)029:8: dkar gsum mngar gsum bcas mar khus spags pas bkang ba bsham /
NK041(di)029:12: shing tog bzang po'i khu ba'i rigs /
NK041(di)029:13: chu gtsang dri bzang lnga tshan lnga sbyar ba bcas kyis bkang ba'i zhal bu gral stabs su 'god /
NK041(di)029:14: phyi nang gi phyogs gang bder shing sna'i me dang /
NK041(di)029:15: rol mo'i rigs byed sogs 'dir mkho ba'i yo byad rnams 'du byas nas /
NK041(di)029:17: 'di nyid lha bsang rgyag barngana sogs bsang gzhung gzhan
NK041(di)029:18: gyi khongs su bsgrub na sngon rjes kyi chos rnams
NK041(di)029:19: zur du mi dgos pas mnol bsang dngos la 'jug
NK041(di)029:20: pas chog cing / 'di kho na sger du gtong skabs su /
NK041(di)029:21: thog mar sbyor ba'i chos mdor bsdus ni /
NK041(di)029:23: bdag sogs 'gro kun deng nas byang chub bar //
NK041(di)029:24: bla ma rtsa gsum lha la skyabs su mchi //
NK041(di)029:25: gzhan don rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob bya'i phyir //
NK041(di)029:26: zab mo'i rnal 'byor bsgom par sems bskyed do //
NK041(di)029:28: ka dag chos sku'i dbyings las 'gags med rtsal //
NK041(di)029:29: pad+ma thod phreng dkar dmar gzhon tshul mdzes //
NK041(di)029:30: mtshan dpe'i gzi 'bar rdo rje thod pa bsnams //
NK041(di)029:31: mdzes brjid rgyan dang cha byad yongs su rdzogs //
NK041(di)029:32: dam ye dbyer med rgyal kun 'dus pa'i gzugs //
NK041(di)029:33: 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi dpal chen por gyur //
NK041(di)029:34: +aahmh'u badz+ra gu ru pad+ma sid+d+hi h'u /
NK041(di)029:35: zhes brgya rtsa sogs bzlas mthar /
NK041(di)029:36: bsang rdzas rnams la bsang chu 'thor zhing /
NK041(di)029:39: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+au las byung ba'i rin po
NK041(di)029:40: che las grub pa'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i
NK041(di)029:41: nang du ahmh'u 'od du zhu ba las byung ba'i
NK041(di)029:42: lha rdzas dri bzang gi mchod pa /
NK041(di)029:43: rtsi shing sna tshogs kyi dud pa /
NK041(di)029:44: zhal zas phye mar gyi 'o skol /
NK041(di)029:45: gsur gyi dud sprin chen po /
NK041(di)029:46: du ba ye shes kyi bdud rtsis sa dang bar snang thams cad gang ba /
NK041(di)029:55: ri rgyal las dpangs mtho ba /
NK041(di)029:56: rgya mtsho las gting zab pa /
NK041(di)029:57: zhing rdul las grangs mang ba /
NK041(di)029:59: rgya che nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa /
NK041(di)029:61: 'chi ba bslu ba'i bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK041(di)029:62: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya lan bdun gyis byin brlab la /
NK041(di)029:63: badz+ra s+pha ra na kham gis spel /
NK041(di)029:65: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dang ni //
NK041(di)029:66: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK041(di)029:67: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs rnams kyis //
NK041(di)029:68: sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK041(di)029:69: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK041(di)029:70: de dag thams cad ci rigs pa //
NK041(di)029:71: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK041(di)029:73: de nas mnol bsang lha chab sngon mo'i gzhung la 'jug /
NK041(di)029:74: skabs su bsang kha gso zhing skyems rigs rnams thab tu 'thor /
NK041(di)029:77: 'byung po gang dag 'dir ni lhag gyur tam //
NK041(di)029:78: sa 'am 'on te bar snang 'khod kyang rung //
NK041(di)029:79: skye rgu rnams la rtag tu byams byed cing //
NK041(di)029:80: nyin dang mtshan du chos la spyod par shog /
NK041(di)029:81: 'dir ni rgyal ba dgra rgyal bden gang gis //
NK041(di)029:82: shin tu bden par gsungs shing rdzun med pa //
NK041(di)029:83: bden pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)029:84: deng kun 'jigs pa che las thar gyur cig /
NK041(di)029:85: ces sogs smon lam gdab cing shis pa brjod pas mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK041(di)029:86: zhes pa'ang rang gzhan grong sngags pa rnams 'jug bde'i
